doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Onboarding - Community
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/styles.css")

  body
    header
      h1 Welcome to the Main Community!
      p Thank you for joining our community. We are excited to have you with us!

    section.main-community
      h2 Main Community Overview
      p Our community focuses on collaboration, knowledge sharing, and growth. Below are some sub-communities you might be interested in, depending on your skills.

    section.sub-communities
      h2 Explore Sub-Communities Based on Your Skills

      ul
        li
          h3 Web Development
          p For developers interested in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and more.
          a(href="/sub-communities/web-development") Join Web Dev Community
          
        li
          h3 Data Science & Machine Learning
          p For those working with data analysis, Python, AI, and machine learning models.
          a(href="/sub-communities/data-science") Join Data Science Community

        li
          h3 Blockchain & Cryptography
          p If you are into decentralized technologies and cryptography, this is the sub-community for you.
          a(href="/sub-communities/blockchain") Join Blockchain Community

        li
          h3 Design & UX
          p Interested in user experience, interface design, and creative solutions? Check this sub-community out.
          a(href="/sub-communities/design") Join Design & UX Community

        li
          h3 DevOps & Cloud Infrastructure
          p For those working on cloud infrastructure, automation, CI/CD, and more.
          a(href="/sub-communities/devops") Join DevOps Community

        li
          h3 AI & Robotics
          p Passionate about artificial intelligence, robotics, and automation?
          a(href="/sub-communities/ai-robotics") Join AI & Robotics Community

    footer
      p If you're unsure where to start, feel free to reach out to one of our community managers for guidance.
      a(href="/contact") Contact Us
